    {
      "id": "1ab4750c-f3ba-80cf-a9c3-e9cb769ec118",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The authors propose an attention-based model to create embeddings of learner code AND a separate set of embeddings encoding skills. Then authors combine DKT to show this representation outperforms the traditional approach.",
